						               													<description>Contame: Terror (Tell me: Horror) is a narrative game, in which a player draws a card from deck &amp;quot;Histories&amp;quot;. Then, he chooses one from deck &amp;quot;Actions&amp;quot; and five from deck &amp;quot;Draws&amp;quot;. He must create a story using elements from all the cards, that includes a number of points awarded to the story-teller by the other players if he uses them correctly. With fearsome characters, chilling settings, very scary objects and special effects to create and tell the best horror stories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After everybody has been the story-teller, the person with more points is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Before starting, you have to divide the deck into four groups: &amp;laquo;Characters&amp;raquo;, &amp;laquo;Scenarios&amp;raquo;, &amp;laquo;Animals + Objects&amp;raquo; and &amp;laquo;Special Effects&amp;raquo;. Then each deck is shuffled well and placed face down on the table. The objective will be to tell a horror story. We suggest three ways to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
